data.description: Welcome to your new spacious 5 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom home in sought after Marywood.  This home has an open concept main level layout.  Gourmet Kitchen with Granite countertops, double wall ovens, gas cooktop, dishwasher and microwave.  LVP throughout 1st and second floors. 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms upstairs along with loft space will give everyone the space they want.  In-Law Suite on Basement/Walk-out level has living area, kitchen, bathroom, bedroom and walk in closet.  Home has solar panels, tankless water heater, garage freezer. You need to see this one right away. Programable thermostat and rain harvesting containers.
